  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

  <h2>Is FreeGenAI really free?</h2>
  <p>Yes. You can generate images without signing up, up to your daily limit. No hidden charges.</p>

  <h2>Do I need to create an account?</h2>
  <p>No, you can start generating images immediately. Creating an account (coming soon) will increase your daily limit.</p>

  <h2>Who owns the images I generate?</h2>
  <p>You are free to use the images you generate for personal or commercial purposes. Please review our AI provider's usage policies for any additional restrictions.</p>

  <h2>Is there a daily limit?</h2>
  <p>Yes, to keep the service free and available for everyone, there's a daily generation limit. Signed-up users get a higher limit than guests.</p>

  <h2>What is "Character Consistency"?</h2>
  <p>It lets you generate a new image using a previous image as a visual reference, helping keep the same character or style across multiple generations.</p>

  <h2>Can I use FreeGenAI for commercial projects?</h2>
  <p>Generally yes, but we recommend reviewing generated content before commercial use, as AI-generated images can occasionally include unintended elements.</p>

